(1145, 1, '2014-12-15 02:13:42', '2014-12-15 02:13:42', 'Offering views of Mont Blanc, this hotel is located in the centre of Chamonix, 950 metres from the Aiguille du Midi cable car. It offers a restaurant, bar and hot tub.\n\nHôtel Alpina offers rooms facing Le Brévent or Mont Blanc. All rooms feature a TV and a minibar and some offer a balcony.\n\nA buffet breakfast is served each morning at the hotel. The Alpina’s restaurant “Le Vista” offers mountain views and serves an all-you-can-eat surf and turf buffet.\n\nIn the evening, guests are invited to relax in the hotel’s bar and lounge with a fireplace. A billiards room is also available.\n\nThe hotel’s reception desk is open 24 hours a day and each Saturday staff organise a welcome meeting to familiarise guests with Chamonix and the surrounding area. Excursions can be organised at the hotel.\n\nThe property is located just across the road from the bus stop. Guests can take the bus to the Brevent Cable Car and join the Les Flegères slopes, the Les Grand Montets slopes and the Les Houches slopes', 'Hôtel Alpina', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hotel-alpina', '', '', '2014-12-15 02:13:42', '2014-12-15 02:13:42', '', 0, 'http://www.soaptheme.net/wordpress/travelo/?post_type=accommodation&amp;p=1145', 0, 'accommodation', '', 0),
