(1159, 1, '2014-10-16 16:54:53', '2014-10-16 16:54:53', 'With direct access to Biscarrosse Lake beach and located a 30-minute drive from Biscarrosse Atlantic Ocean beach, Abc Vacances Discount features an outdoor and an indoor swimming pool. This holiday park also offers free WiFi access in public areas.\n\nViewing the property garden filled with pine trees, each accommodation is air conditioned and includes a seating area with a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower, toilet and a hairdryer.\n\nGuests can have their meals at Abc Vacances Discount restaurant or sip a drink at the bar. Meals can also be prepared in the mobile homes’ fully equipped kitchenette and barbecue facilities are at guests\' disposal.\n\nAt an extra cost, scuba diving, fishing, water sport activities, table tennis, mini golf, windsurfing, billiards and a tennis court can be enjoyed on site. Bicycles rental is possible and biking roads can be found nearby. Labouheyre Train Station is located 30 km from Abc Vacances Discount.', 'Abc Vacances Discount', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'abc-vacances-discount', '', '', '2014-10-16 16:54:53', '2014-10-16 16:54:53', '', 0, 'http://www.soaptheme.net/wordpress/travelo/?post_type=accommodation&amp;p=1159', 0, 'accommodation', '', 0),
